        </p>
        <h3>Bruce Bell</h3>
        <p>
          My background was as a lawyer before moving to work in the areas of law enforcement and defence.  I have always had a passion for the Word of God and this led to further study in theology and biblical studies.  As well as a degree in Law I also have a Post Graduate Diploma in Theology and a PhD in Theology.  I was the teaching pastor at another church before becoming part of the team at The Olive Tree.  I have an abiding interest in philosophy/worldviews, history, science and hermeneutics (interpreting scripture).  Apart from shepherding God’s people on a daily basis and watching them grow and develop, I love nothing more than being able to preach and teach His Word.
